					<!-- CONTENT -->
					<div id="content_section" class="ra-flex-item-dynamic">
						<h1>Restart the activation services</h1>
<p>Restart the FactoryTalk Activation services if you cannot refresh the server using the <strong><strong>Refresh</strong></strong> button, or activations do not appear after adding a new activation server.</p>
<h2>To restart the activation services:</h2>
<ol>
<li>Open the Windows <strong><strong>Control Panel</strong></strong>, then click <strong><strong>Administrative Tools &gt; Services</strong></strong>.</li>
<li>Right-click <strong>FactoryTalk Activation Helper</strong>, and click <strong><strong>Restart</strong></strong>.</li>
<li>Right-click <strong>FactoryTalk Activation Service</strong>, and click <strong><strong>Restart</strong></strong>.</li>
</ol>
<h2>See also</h2>
<p class="seealso"><a id="h22822" class="jumptemplate" title="Configure the FactoryTalk Activation server" href="22785.htm" target="_self">Configure the FactoryTalk Activation server</a></p>
